graph LR
    ODH[ODH Notebook Controller]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    ODH -->|watches CRs| KubeflowCtrl[Kubeflow Notebook Controller v1]
    ODH -->|creates HTTPRoutes| GatewayAPI[Gateway API v1.2.1]
    ODH -->|provisions certs| ServiceCA[OpenShift Service CA 4.19+]
    ODH -->|injects sidecar| KubeRBACProxy[kube-rbac-proxy]
    ODH -->|API operations| K8s[Kubernetes 1.33+]
    ODH -->|OpenShift APIs| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.19+]
    ODH -->|controller framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime v0.21.0]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    ODH -->|routes traffic| DSGateway[Data Science Gateway]
    ODH -->|provisions secrets| DSPipelines[Data Science Pipelines Operator]
    ODH -.->|UI creates CRs| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    ODH -->|mounts CA bundle| TrustedCA[Trusted CA Bundle]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard -->|creates| NotebookCR[Notebook CR]
    NotebookCR -->|watched by| ODH
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -->|auto deploy| ODH

    %% External Services
    ODH -->|pulls images| ImageRegistry[Image Registry]
    ODH -->|OAuth integration| OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth]
    ODH -->|proxy config| ProxyServer[OpenShift Proxy]

    %% Runtime Dependencies
    KubeRBACProxy -->|authenticates| K8s
    GatewayAPI -->|implemented by| DSGateway
    ServiceCA -->|rotates certs| TLSSecrets[TLS Secrets]
    TLSSecrets -->|used by| KubeRBACProxy

    %% Component Internal Flow
    ODH -->|creates| HTTPRoute[HTTPRoute CRD]
    ODH -->|creates| ReferenceGrant[ReferenceGrant CRD]
    ODH -->|creates| NetworkPolicy[NetworkPolicy]
    ODH -->|creates| ServiceAccount[ServiceAccount]
    ODH -->|creates| Role[Role/RoleBinding]

    HTTPRoute -->|routes to| DSGateway
    ReferenceGrant -->|permits| HTTPRoute
    NetworkPolicy -->|isolates| NotebookPod[Notebook Pod]
    ServiceAccount -->|authenticates| NotebookPod

    %% Styling
    style ODH fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    style KubeflowCtrl fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style GatewayAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style ServiceCA fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style KubeRBACProxy fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style K8s fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style OpenShift fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style ControllerRuntime fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    style DSGateway fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style DSPipelines fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style TrustedCA fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style Pipelines fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000

    %% External Services
